{"tid":826474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹災後】4架新巴九巴城巴行車相繼損毀 遭大樹壓毀車頂 乘客嚇餐飽","createTime":"2018-09-18T09:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T12:11:17.000Z","uid":22349,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"793a36399977ab3726758845f38463cb7033b8d4","tid":826474,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"風災過後，各區仍有大量樹木折斷阻路，更有部分椏枝造成障礙，雖然各部門已盡力清理，道路大致通暢，但即使通車後仍有行車線被大樹等雜物阻擋。今(18日)早11時許，一輛85號路線九巴，在總站開出後，駛至火炭路近山尾街時，車頂撞到塌下樹幹，導致車身受損，車長停車報案，意外中無人受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n另外2宗分別發生於將軍澳及九龍城。早上9時許，一輛93K路線九巴，駛經寶林北路時，車頭撞到路邊塌下的樹椏，部分樹椏插入擋風玻璃，車長發現即時停車報警，意外中無人受傷。早上8時許，有巿民乘搭1號線九巴沿太子道西往旺角時，稱巴士被大樹擊中，以致上層車頭擋風玻璃裂開損毀，乘客通知車長，事件中幸無人受傷，巴士其後返回車廠維修。 <br />\n<br />\n而除九巴外，一輛118號路線城巴，今晨8時許，由小西灣開出往長沙灣，期間有中途乘客上車時發現車頂被一條長約1.5米的樹枝插穿，樹枝跌在上層近車尾位置座椅上，乘客通知車長，但巴士繼續行駛，直至巴士駛至長沙灣後，車長將樹枝移走，然後將車駛回車廠維修。"},{"pid":"eb87a6a7e7b723596a7b82f8b8464be99b9deb8c","tid":826474,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"一輛新巴沿柴灣道行駛，至興華邨對開時，路邊一棵大樹突然塌下，壓毀上層車頂。(fb「柴灣人柴灣事」群組圖片)<br />\n<br />\n山竹席捲本港期間，多區有樹木倒塌橫亙路中，數以百計道路封閉，雖然工人已經疲於奔命清理塌樹，但柴灣下午發生塌樹意外，一輛駛至的新巴遭壓頂！下午3時許，一輛新巴沿柴灣道行駛，至興華邨對開時，路邊一棵大樹突然塌下，壓毀上層車頂，司機立即停車報警。警方及消防接報到場，正壓住巴士頂的樹枝移走，事件中未知有無人受傷。"},{"pid":"e362f75830ca7c9895607809995624b095fc2778","tid":826474,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/photo/bkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180918133525\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180918%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180918133525&h=ecad3965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/photo/bkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180918133525\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180918%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180918133525&h=6d885c42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/photo/bkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180918133525\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180918%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180918101832837-0918_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180918133525&h=3596f56a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dcb912fd173feeef058603af680bfc510ee828e","tid":826474,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/172013_4584b4cff0667c77406194683b39e197.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F172013_4584b4cff0667c77406194683b39e197.png&h=d87d46cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4cfb8021029a50b15a22915e4cd12bec875d62e","tid":826474,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2160000/2163366/BB_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2160000%2F2163366%2FBB_600.jpg&h=05e14a27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a04089b48a5b064a8f9ab12c325e36d8240ecf5d","tid":826474,"uid":14912,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:22:06.000Z","msg":"連環跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ae06e4adff5d0511939eb96c43a07587643be0","tid":826474,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:22:19.000Z","msg":"好彩冇人死"},{"pid":"225ea83da420e0555a8ed45c34321637dd4a24c5","tid":826474,"uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537239293_19ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537239293_19ad.jpg&h=1c0b84cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537231514_b205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537231514_b205.jpg&h=5f2aea4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537231518_07cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537231518_07cd.jpg&h=d13872fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n. 今早8時左右，在柴灣環翠邨登乘118線城巴過九龍，走到上層，赫然發現尾排第三座位，有一條約1.5米長的樹枝掉在座椅和地上，對上車頂位置穿了洞，露出隔熱棉。<br />\n<br />\n黃小姐以為是剛才發生的事，車長不知情，於是通知車長。不料車長反應冷淡，繼續行車。黃小姐感到奇怪，只是見沒有乘客受傷，她到油麻地眾坊街便落車。<br />\n<br />\n118線由小西灣(藍灣半島)開出，終站是長沙灣(深旺道)。記者稍後在旺角荔枝角道找到該城巴，當時車長已經通知控制室，他把樹枝移走放到路面，然後將巴士駛回車廠維修。"},{"pid":"b09504ef1d71db6234ce650482413edce66cc268","tid":826474,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"巴士連環跳樓"},{"pid":"7cd49e9f1432667a7c62dd8646016d957bb952a7","tid":826474,"uid":188282,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:31:05.000Z","msg":"根本d樹一早冧左架喇。巴士跳樓啫。"},{"pid":"cde3b8a00a8e95ef2086562c7a3e16464a34f159","tid":826474,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a060a7305f849945441708d20c9d326f7670a6d5","tid":826474,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34644f3419fd6d7f6a91097aa958da8d147c0ff7","tid":826474,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:36:59.000Z","msg":